tachment','image/jpeg',0),(182,1,'2015-06-28 10:13:23','2015-06-28 10:13:23','','trj header5','','inherit','open','open','','trj-header5','','','2015-06-28 10:13:23','2015-06-28 10:13:23','',0,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/trj-header5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(183,1,'2015-06-28 10:14:06','2015-06-28 10:14:06','','trj header6','','inherit','open','open','','trj-header6','','','2015-06-28 10:14:06','2015-06-28 10:14:06','',0,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/trj-header6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(184,1,'2015-06-28 10:14:39','2015-06-28 10:14:39','','trj header7','','inherit','open','open','','trj-header7','','','2015-06-28 10:14:39','2015-06-28 10:14:39','',0,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/trj-header7.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(185,1,'2015-06-28 10:18:59','2015-06-28 10:18:59','','about banner','','inherit','open','open','','about-banner','','','2015-06-28 10:18:59','2015-06-28 10:18:59','',112,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/about-banner.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(186,1,'2015-06-28 13:35:13','2015-06-28 13:35:13','<p><a href=\"http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/about-banner.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" src=\"http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/about-banner.jpg\" alt=\"about banner\" width=\"1340\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p>Trousseau helps you make a style statement on one of the most important days in your life. We aim to bring out the best in you with an exotic collection of clothes, accessories and gift ideas. Trousseau by RJ gives personalised attention to Trousseau planning and indirect wedding consultations, easing out an important part of the event, allowing you to focus on the numerous other matters associated with a wedding.</p>\n<p>Styling is an art form, that on one hand, is highly personal and individualistic, yet it also depends on the respective families and the broader cultural context. We firmly believe that everybody needs a different combination, customised to their personality and family, and we aim to help you find it. At TRJ, we employ experts that combine a natural flair for style with years of experience in fashion and marriages to help you pull off your dream wedding.</p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>About RJ</strong></em></span></h2>\n<p>As a child, Ritu Jain (aka RJ) had a natural eye for elegance and detailing. This helped her to appreciate creativity and style in everything from clothes, stones, precious metal or in jewellery.</p>\n<p>RJ later learnt the details required for perfect styling, like the graceful silhouette that accentuates the Indian figure, and how the appropriate fabric and colour combinations enhance the exquisiteness of the design. She also intuitively understood how to complement clothing with jewellery, keeping in mind colour, intricacy, and the material.</p>\n<p>After years of practise and praise, RJ began by designing and manufacturing jewellery in her own unique style, before she finally started using her creativity and imagination to help several brides collect their best trousseau.</p>\n<h2><em><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Why Choose TRJ?</strong></span></em></h2>\n<p>Choosing the right attire for the big day and pairing it up with the right accessories from exclusive wedding trousseau gives the whole look a more personal touch, something that TRJ understands instinctively. Apart from providing exclusive Trousseau consulting and Trousseau planning services, we also offer a variety of other services depending upon the needs of the client.</p>\n<p>We design the most exclusive and unique trousseaus with the ideal elements suiting your personality. From jewellery to clothes, to silver, to personal items, TRJ helps you in planning, purchasing and presenting the perfect bridal trousseau.</p>\n<p>As a reporter for fashion week, RJ has had a lot of experience in learning and observing styles/trends from various fashion capitals across the globe, and has the ability to transform people by selecting the right clothes and accessories.</p>\n<p>Our exclusive, one of a kind wedding service of trousseau consultation, planning and shopping has been acclaimed by all of our customers from different walks of life.</p>\n<p>If you have a dream trousseau, we can help you make that dream come to reality.</p>\n','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','112-autosave-v1','','','2015-06-28 13:35:13','2015-06-28 13:35:13','',112,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/2015/06/28/112-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(187,1,'2015-06-28 10:21:59','2015-06-28 10:21:59','<a href=\"http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/about-banner.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" src=\"http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/about-banner.jpg\" alt=\"about banner\" width=\"1340\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTrousseau helps you make a style statement on one of the most important days in your life. We aim to bring out the best in you with an exotic collection of clothes, accessories and gift ideas. Trousseau by RJ gives personalised attention to Trousseau planning and indirect wedding consultations, easing out an important part of the event, allowing you to focus on the numerous other matters associated with a wedding.\r\n\r\nStyling is an art form, that on one hand, is highly personal and individualistic, yet it also depends on the respective families and the broader cultural context. We firmly believe that everybody needs a different combination, customised to their personality and family, and we aim to help you find it. At TRJ, we employ experts that combine a natural flair for style with years of experience in fashion and marriages to help you pull off your dream wedding.\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>About RJ</strong></em></span></h2>\r\nAs a child, Ritu Jain (aka RJ) had a natural eye for elegance and detailing. This helped her to appreciate creativity and style in everything from clothes, stones, precious metal or in jewellery.\r\n\r\nRJ later learnt the details required for perfect styling, like the graceful silhouette that accentuates the Indian figure, and how the appropriate fabric and colour combinations enhance the exquisiteness of the design. She also intuitively understood how to complement clothing with jewellery, keeping in mind colour, intricacy, and the material.\r\n\r\nAfter years of practise and praise, RJ began by designing and manufacturing jewellery in her own unique style, before she finally started using her creativity and imagination to help several brides collect their best trousseau.\r\n<h2><em><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Why Choose TRJ?</strong></span></em></h2>\r\nChoosing the right attire for the big day and pairing it up with the right accessories from exclusive wedding trousseau gives the whole look a more personal touch, something that TRJ understands instinctively. Apart from providing exclusive Trousseau consulting and Trousseau planning services, we also offer a variety of other services depending upon the needs of the client.\r\n\r\nWe design the most exclusive and unique trousseaus with the ideal elements suiting your personality. From jewellery to clothes, to silver, to personal items, TRJ helps you in planning, purchasing and presenting the perfect bridal trousseau.\r\n\r\nAs a reporter for fashion week, RJ has had a lot of experience in learning and observing styles/trends from various fashion capitals across the globe, and has the ability to transform people by selecting the right clothes and accessories.\r\n\r\nOur exclusive, one of a kind wedding service of trousseau consultation, planning and shopping has been acclaimed by all of our customers from different walks of life.\r\n\r\nIf you have a dream trousseau, we can help you make that dream come to reality.','About Us','','inherit','open','open'