 finest wedding trousseau\r\n\r\nTo deliver a personal experience, we follow a detailed process that includes multiple one-on-one meetings with the bride and the family members in order to determine the requirements for the wedding trousseau.\r\n<h3><strong>Personalized Shopping Consultancy</strong></h3>\r\nIndian weddings are all about flaunting the best dresses and finest accessories. We, at Trousseau by RJ, possess style experts who assist you in shopping for your <strong>exclusive wedding trousseau </strong>and <strong>bridal ensembles </strong>that perfectly match your personality while helping you make a unique style statement.\r\n<h3><strong>Trousseau shopping</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>Trousseau shopping</strong> is often considered as a tiresome activity, where one needs to pay attention to the latest trends and what suits an individual. Our team of style experts understand your personality and thus, make you shop for only the best products that will enhance your looks for your special day and for the days to come with the best bridal trousseau\r\n<h3><strong>Securing Purchases</strong></h3>\r\nOur in-depth knowledge of the market and understanding of current fashion trends allows you to secure your purchases and helps you buy products of the best quality.\r\n<h3><strong>Shopping of the finest items within the budget</strong></h3>\r\nWe provide customised services, helping you fetch the best products well within your budget range. We do not let our clients compromise with style or fashion due to budget limitations.','SERVICES','','inherit','open','open','','146-revision-v1','','','2015-06-28 13:42:50','2015-06-28 13:42:50','',146,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/2015/06/28/146-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(198,1,'2015-06-28 13:44:29','2015-06-28 13:44:29','','testimonials banner','','inherit','open','open','','testimonials-banner','','','2015-06-28 13:44:29','2015-06-28 13:44:29','',150,'http://192.185.26.69/~trjqa/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/testimonials-bann